channel.title: Volunteering myself
channel.description:
After a long brake, I would like to offer myself in service.
I would like to join a team of developers who are coding their RSPS for public release.
* I am not a good coder, I know just basics, how to add teleport commands and so on. * I have 32 GB vps, I use it for mw2 servers and couple mc servers for my other gaming clan, I offer VPS for the website and server. * If no one want's me, I am looking for coders then who would like a new project.
If this is in inappropriate place to advertise myself please feel free to move it. Contact me on skype or in this comment if you willing to accept offer ( SKYPE NAME ) robertasvin
